*''Combinatorics: Room Squares, Sum-Free Sets, Hadamard Matrices'' (with W. D. Wallis and [[Jennifer Seberry|Jennifer Seberry Wallis]], Springer, Lecture Notes in Mathematics 292, 1972){{r|payne}}
*''Combinatorial Theory: An Introduction'' (with W. D. Wallis, Charles Babbage Research Centre, 1977){{r|sheehan}}
